  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introdução a Speex</title>

    <para>
      <application>Speex</application> is an audio compression format designed
specifically for speech. It is well-adapted to internet applications and
provides useful features that are not present in most other CODECs.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

